#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _versions/main/guides/security-spiffe-client.adoc
msgid "SPIFFE Client"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-spiffe-client.adoc
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-experimental\" title=\"This extension requests early feedback to mature the idea\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">experimental</a>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-spiffe-client.adoc
msgid ""
"https://spiffe.io/[SPIFFE] (Secure Production Identity Framework for Everyone) provides cryptographic workload identities in zero-trust environments.\n"
"The SPIFFE client extension uses the https://github.com/spiffe/spiffe/blob/main/standards/SPIFFE_Workload_API.md[Workload API] to retrieve https://github.com/spiffe/spiffe/blob/main/standards/JWT-SVID.md[JWT Verifiable Identity Documents (JWT-SVIDs)] for Quarkus workloads directly from the local https://spiffe.io/docs/latest/spire-about/spire-concepts/[SPIRE Agent].\n"
"It simplifies deployment by eliminating the need for a SPIFFE client sidecar that stores JWT-SVIDs on a mounted file path for Quarkus to read."
msgstr ""

